1. *Odlazi* se iz grada. (He is leaving the city.) 
2. Ona *odlazi* ranije sutra. (She is leaving earlier tomorrow.) 
3. On *odlazi* na put. (He is going on a trip.)
4. Oni se *odlaze* odavde. (They are leaving from here.)
5. Ona *odlaže* svoje planove. (She is postponing her plans.)
6. Oni *odlažu* sastanak. (They are postponing the meeting.)
7. On *odlazi* u školu. (He is going to school.)
8. Oni *odlaze* na more. (They are going to the sea.)